OL,3,CFormer Co-op Bank boss jailed for
OL,4,Cthree years over #100,000 fraud
OL,6,FITV News' North of England reporter
OL,7,FAmy Welch has the latest from
OL,8,FManchester Crown Court.
OL,10,FFormer Co-operative Bank chairman Paul
OL,11,FFlowers ` who stole nearly #100,000
OL,12,Ffrom an elderly woman to spend on
OL,13,Fdrugs, holidays and gifts for himself
OL,14,F` has been jailed for three years.
OL,16,FFlowers, 74, a former Labour
OL,17,Fcouncillor and church minister, had
OL,18,Fbetrayed his friend of many years,
OL,19,FMargaret Jarvis, to plunder her cash,
OL,20,FManchester Crown Court heard.
