OL,4,Cthree years over #100,000 fraud
OL,6,FFlowers, dubbed the "Crystal
OL,7,FMethodist" after a newspaper drugs
OL,8,Fsting, had been made power of attorney
OL,9,Fand executor of the will of Miss
OL,10,FJarvis, a teetotal retired teacher,
OL,11,Fwho never married and had no children.
OL,13,FHis public profile helped his friend
OL,14,Ftrust him with her affairs, the court
OL,15,Fheard.
