OL,3,CFormer Co-op Bank boss jailed for
OL,4,Cthree years over #100,000 fraud
OL,6,FBut as Miss Jarvis's dementia
OL,7,Fprogressed and she could no longer
OL,8,Flook after her own money, Flowers
OL,9,Fbegan controlling her accounts and
OL,10,Fusing her cash for his own selfish
OL,11,Fends, the court heard.
OL,13,FHe continued taking her cash after her
OL,14,Fdeath, aged 82, in 2016 in a care home
OL,15,Fnear Amersham, in Buckinghamshire.
OL,17,FFlowers, from Salford, Greater
OL,18,FManchester, had admitted 18 counts of
OL,19,Ffraud at an earlier hearing, amounting
OL,20,Fto nearly #100,000 over a two-year
OL,21,Fperiod ending in 2017.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
