OL,6,F"In truth, you knew all along she
OL,7,Fcould not, because of your own
OL,8,Fweaknesses and failings."
OL,10,FEarlier Joe Allman, prosecuting, told
OL,11,Fthe court that Flowers and Miss Jarvis
OL,12,Fbecame friends through charity work
OL,13,Fthey were both involved in, building a
OL,14,Fhome for poor children in
OL,15,FJohannesburg, South Africa.
