OL,6,FThey also went on holidays together
OL,7,Fand in 1995 while Miss Jarvis was
OL,8,Fstill of sound mind she gave Flowers
OL,9,Fpower of attorney to look after her
OL,10,Ffinancial affairs if she became
OL,11,Fincapable, Mr Allman said, adding: "No
OL,12,Fdoubt her decision would have been
OL,13,Finfluenced by Mr Flowers then high-
OL,14,Fstanding in the community, a minister,
OL,15,Flocal councillor and non-executive
OL,16,Fdirector of the Co-op Bank.
