OL,6,F"Flowers was dubbed the "Crystal
OL,7,FMethodist" after the Mail on Sunday
OL,8,Fpublished secretly filmed footage of
OL,9,Fthe then-church minister handing over
OL,10,F#300 in cash for crystal meth and
OL,11,Fother drugs in Leeds in November 2013.
OL,13,FHe pleaded guilty at Leeds
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court to possessing
OL,15,Fcocaine, crystal meth and ketamine,
OL,16,Fand was fined #400.
