OL,6,FAn analysis of transactions by Flowers
OL,7,Fshowed he had used Miss Jarvis's money
OL,8,Fto buy theatre tickets, fine wines,
OL,9,Fcruise holidays, stays at the Park
OL,10,FHotel in Knightsbridge and tickets for
OL,11,Fthe West End show, Jersey Boys.
OL,13,FHe had also spent her money
OL,14,Fwithdrawing cash for shopping,
OL,15,Finstalling a #14,900 bespoke staircase
OL,16,Fat his home and #1,275 for a carpet.
OL,18,FHe also spent money on drugs, the
OL,19,Fcourt heard, with only one of Miss
OL,20,FJarvis's two nieces receiving the
OL,21,F#10,000 she had left in her will.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
