OL,6,FBob Elias, defending, said Flowers had
OL,7,Fled a life of "significant
OL,8,Fachievement" but had suffered a
OL,9,F"remarkable fall from grace".
OL,11,FHe said Flowers, a grammar school boy
OL,12,Fafter passing his 11 plus, had "found
OL,13,Fhis vocation" after studying theology
OL,14,Fat Bristol University and became
OL,15,Fordained as a Methodist minister in
OL,16,F1978, later rising to the top in the
OL,17,Fbanking industry, becoming boss of the
OL,18,FCo-op Bank in 2010, but had struggled
OL,19,Fwith his sexuality.
