OL,6,FMr Elias continued: "As he became a
OL,7,Fpublic figure he found it nigh on
OL,8,Fimpossible to 'come out'. The persona
OL,9,Fone has as a clergyman or high
OL,10,Fofficial in a bank makes it difficult.
OL,11,FThat stress or tension was there for
OL,12,Fmuch of his life."
OL,14,FHe said the pressure led to his
OL,15,Fincreased use of cocaine, until the
OL,16,Fnewspaper sting revealed his drug use.
OL,18,FMr Elias added: "He will bear with him
OL,19,Ftill the day he dies the sobriquet,
OL,20,FCrystal Methodist."
